{"title":"小河","authors":["郑渊洁"],"dates":[{"year":1980,"month":8,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"小河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京大华无线电仪器厂  郑渊洁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗沙粒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞进了小伙子的眼窝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真没想到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它竟成了爱情的使者。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车间里这么多姑娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小伙子专请那一个。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说来奇怪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他自己也不知为什么。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"棉纱擦掉手上的污浊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她又打了三遍肥皂还不嫌多。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘也曾惊奇地发现，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自己爱偷偷看他干活……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把眼皮轻轻翻起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘的手微微哆嗦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小伙子还是感觉到了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽管很弱很弱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她第一次这样盯着他的眼睛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仔细地寻找那位不速之客。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在他的瞳孔中看到了自己，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发现里边有条爱情的小河……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}